{"tid":2419680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉港台疆藏企硬 王毅籲美回歸理性  學者：老調重彈無反思","createTime":"2021-02-23T12:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T13:25:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"164e94874575e4a63bdb8c5e4586b7e6b19e7812","tid":2419680,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210223/4GIOX22QZRBB7NZQSWSL7T7SKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210223%2F4GIOX22QZRBB7NZQSWSL7T7SKA%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3wy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=4d309ace\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210223%2F4GIOX22QZRBB7NZQSWSL7T7SKA%2F&h=9aa5cf59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210223/4GIOX22QZRBB7NZQSWSL7T7SKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n涉港台疆藏企硬 王毅籲美回歸理性 <br />\n學者：老調重彈無反思<br />\n<br />\n美國政府換屆後對華政策基調未變，中國國務委員兼外長王毅昨向拜登政府喊話，不點名地指中美關係陷入低谷的根源在於美國特朗普前政府「出於自身政治需要」，對華作出各種遏制打壓行徑，呼籲美國新政府「推動對華政策回歸理性」。但學者批評王毅的說法只是老調重彈，未有反思雙邊關係惡化的原因。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「工業規模」虐待維人 藍韜文促聯國徹查<br />\n<br />\n王毅昨出席在外交部大樓舉行的藍廳論壇開幕式並致辭，大批親華外國前政經名人獲邀作視像致辭，包括美國前財政部長保爾森、澳洲前總理陸克文、美國國際集團（AIG）前行政總裁格林伯格（Maurice Greenberg）等作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zwD7rKdglxqZ2TS1MSP_wpQnBKs=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3VQDADHDHVH6XLXSKG4LOHUU3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzwD7rKdglxqZ2TS1MSP_wpQnBKs%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3VQDADHDHVH6XLXSKG4LOHUU3Q.jpg&h=047b9b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王毅昨在藍廳論壇致辭時呼籲美國新政府推動中美關係重回正軌。法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀撤銷對華制裁<br />\n<br />\n王毅在致辭表示，國家主席習近平在大除夕與拜登進行了首次通話，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美大使崔天凱也在視像致辭時強調，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將雙邊問題歸咎美方<br />\n<br />\n台灣淡江大學中國大陸研究所助理教授曾偉峯對本報稱，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/美國之音"},{"pid":"ddfb7d4177d59a3566ced7792e47f58e346dc067","tid":2419680,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"共產黨點會認錯"},{"pid":"05d5e4695b42f824a74f0bd23ac16c107dbddd29","tid":2419680,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"諗住China Joe會放軟，而家仲諗住玩戰狼外交，喝令人哋聽支那支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪反效果囉！蝗毅玩外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d17aa0ea8b1b6cc6ed6c589ba38cb879139b403","tid":2419680,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05d5e4695b42f824a74f0bd23ac16c107dbddd29","tid":2419680,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"諗住China Joe會放軟，而家仲諗住玩戰狼外交，喝令人哋聽支那支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪反效果囉！蝗毅玩外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:24:20.000Z","msg":"China Joe放軟 即是話俾人知賣國"},{"pid":"7b4eb1a63ae0a65ef950bdde2d35f8010fb4bd5b","tid":2419680,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d17aa0ea8b1b6cc6ed6c589ba38cb879139b403","tid":2419680,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05d5e4695b42f824a74f0bd23ac16c107dbddd29","tid":2419680,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"諗住China Joe會放軟，而家仲諗住玩戰狼外交，喝令人哋聽支那支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪反效果囉！蝗毅玩外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:24:20.000Z","msg":"China Joe放軟 即是話俾人知賣國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"夾到China Joe都無得縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/